01:08:56.522 --> 01:09:02.888
there. He has disadvantage on that, so first, I'm
going to do that with you. Rolled really well with

01:09:02.888 --> 01:09:06.924
disadvantage, natural 19 and a natural 17. Make an
acrobatics or athletics check to see if he doesn't

01:09:06.924 --> 01:09:08.381
grapple you.

01:09:08.381 --> 01:09:11.355
TALIESIN: Acrobatics or athletics? Those are both
