01:09:11.355 --> 01:09:14.576
SAM: You're a big thing.

01:09:14.576 --> 01:09:20.643
TALIESIN: I'm a big thing. A 20 is what I rolled.
I rolled a 19 plus one, so I'm going to do an

01:09:20.643 --> 01:09:21.732
acrobatics run.

01:09:21.732 --> 01:09:22.440
MATT: Okay.

01:09:22.440 --> 01:09:23.897
(laughter)

01:09:23.897 --> 01:09:25.672
TALIESIN: I am, to be fair, invisible. It's hard
