01:09:38.284 --> 01:09:41.081
really confused. For a moment, he thinks it was a
ghost.

01:09:41.081 --> 01:09:43.364
LIAM: Nothing but sparkle pony fur.

01:09:43.364 --> 01:09:46.882
MATT: For the one that rushed up to try to grab
