01:16:17.156 --> 01:16:18.731
SAM: You've got a big stick.

01:16:18.731 --> 01:16:20.308
LAURA: Do not attack them!

01:16:20.308 --> 01:16:22.603
LIAM: Sam Riegel, shut the fuck up!

01:16:22.603 --> 01:16:28.839
MARISHA: I...

01:16:28.839 --> 01:16:29.548
wait.

01:16:29.848 --> 01:16:31.446
TRAVIS: Yeah!

01:16:31.446 --> 01:16:39.198
MATT: The tension in your body is rising up, and
for a second, the muscles bulge and the veins

01:16:39.198 --> 01:16:43.329
begin to pop from the sheer amount of adrenaline
