LAURA: Before everybody gets on the boat, can I
run over to the docks because I'm not shackled,

02:16:53.507 --> 02:16:57.963
and I try to find the jewels that I dumped off the
docks.

02:16:57.963 --> 02:16:59.966
MATT: Okay. You have to dive into the water to do
so.

02:16:59.966 --> 02:17:01.160
LAURA: Okay.

02:17:01.160 --> 02:17:06.946
MATT: So, you jump into the water. Make an
investigation-- No, this'll be a perception check

02:17:06.946 --> 02:17:09.172
with disa-fucking-vantage.

02:17:09.172 --> 02:17:11.051
SAM: Disa-fucking-vantage!

02:17:11.051 --> 02:17:11.763
MATT: Yeah.

02:17:11.763 --> 02:17:13.591
LAURA: Ooh! (laughter)

02:17:13.591 --> 02:17:16.039
TALIESIN: Wow, fuck you!

02:17:16.039 --> 02:17:18.032
LAURA: Two ones!

02:17:18.032 --> 02:17:21.762
LIAM: You counterbalanced the rest of this game!

02:17:21.762 --> 02:17:25.054
TALIESIN: Fucking belly flop into the water!

02:17:25.054 --> 02:17:26.648
TRAVIS: Sin eater!

02:17:26.648 --> 02:17:29.596
SAM: Two ones in a roll.

02:17:29.596 --> 02:17:33.017
LIAM: Has that happened since the walk of shame?

02:17:33.017 --> 02:17:34.303
LAURA: No.

02:17:34.303 --> 02:17:37.678
LIAM: Two years ago.

