02:18:56.342 --> 02:18:57.246
LIAM: No.

02:18:57.246 --> 02:18:58.275
SAM: Yeah, we have our crew.

02:18:58.275 --> 02:18:59.834
LIAM: We have our crew. We do not need them.

02:18:59.834 --> 02:19:01.672
TALIESIN: Yeah, we've got a way.

